- (laughs) Oh, yeah, big time.

04:47.521 --> 04:48.922
(laughing)
- Oh, I know.

04:48.956 --> 04:50.023
- Eat that shit.

04:51.792 --> 04:53.093
- (groans)

04:53.126 --> 04:54.194
- You should probably
get going soon

04:54.227 --> 04:55.796
to that strip club.

04:55.829 --> 04:57.164
