always crazy.

04:57.197 --> 04:58.999
- Yeah, you're right.
(sighs)

04:59.032 --> 05:00.368
- What's the matter?

05:00.401 --> 05:02.336
- I am just dreading
this bachelor party.

05:02.370 --> 05:04.538
I'm gonna be stuck there
all night, unable to leave,

05:04.572 --> 05:07.307
and all I feel like doing
is staying in with you

05:07.341 --> 05:09.176
and watching Shark Tank.
- Oh, come on.

05:09.209 --> 05:11.211
There's plenty of time
to do that.

05:11.244 --> 05:12.680
Relax, go hang out
with Mike.

05:12.713 --> 05:15.282
How bad could it be?

